claim.claim-text:
1. A minimally invasive direct cardiac massage device comprising: 
a handle; 
a structure attached to one end of the handle adapted to contact a pericardium or heart surface to compress the heart; 
a force transducer coupled to the handle or structure to produce a signal which corresponds to an amount of force applied through the handle to the heart; 
a signal processor which receives the force transducer signal and produces an output corresponding to the applied force; and 
a display which receives the output of the signal processor and produces a human decipherable indication based on the applied force.
